	<div class="blog-archive-entries-wrapper">
		<div id="unique-entry-id-283" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Sidoriio's Song</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 31 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ideas/dolphin/dolphin.html" rel="self" title="Dirty Dolphin"><img class="imageStyle" alt="twins" src="twins.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>For all you fans of the <a href="../../../ideas/dolphin/dolphin.html" rel="self" title="Dirty Dolphin">The Dirty Dolphin Jukebox</a> at the Calle del Marinero there is a treat in store at the ViP section (<a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/competitions/tshirtcompetition2010sidorio/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk">www.vampirates.co.uk</a>) in the way of a new competition.<br /><br />They want you to tell them "what song you think best sums up Sidorio, and why"<br /><br />This competition will run from&nbsp;29th January 2010&nbsp;until midnight (GMT) on&nbsp;12th February&nbsp;2010 and is open to international entries.  (Yipee anyone can enter again - off to check out my CDs behind me)<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-282" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">The Honeymooners</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 31 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/girlwiththeblackhearttattoo/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="Empire Of Night" src="Empire.jpg" width="74" height="113" /></a></div>Chapter three has now appeared on the Vampirate.co.uk website.<br /><br /><br /><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-279" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">US Empire Of The Night</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Wednesday, 27 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><img class="imageStyle" alt="Empire Of Night" src="EmpireUS.jpg" width="78" height="113" />According to the Vampirate Blog on <a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/countdowntopublicationbegins/" rel="external" title="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/merrychristmaswritingisover/">www.vampirates.co.uk</a> the UK editor has finished work on the text and now both the UK and US artwork has been released.<br /><br />Just a reminder for everyone in the Americas it has been delayed till published August 1st 2010, Sorry folks I will be waiting here too.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-277" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Mistletoe?</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Wednesday, 27 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-artwork.php">Artwork</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://boblea.deviantart.com/gallery/#Vampirates" rel="external" title="http://boblea.deviantart.com/gallery/#Vampirates"><img class="imageStyle" alt="books" src="books.jpg" width="42" height="40" /></a></div>I was just checking out the links worked on the website and discovered Lorcan got in the mood for Christmas too.<br />Check out <a href="http://boblea.deviantart.com/gallery/#Vampirates" rel="external" title="http://boblea.deviantart.com/gallery/#Vampirates">http://boblea.deviantart.com/gallery/#Vampirates</a><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-276" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Vampirates Central has been updated.</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Wednesday, 27 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>Vampirates.co.uk is enjoying the new year start and have been updating all round the website.  From a new blog entry to the updated countdown widget to extra characters and places added to the website.</div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-273" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">On Twitter</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Tuesday, 26 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>Justin can be found on Twitter and just wrote:<br />"Just been tipped off that VAMPIRATES: BLOOD CAPTAIN is on the SLA's new Everyone's Reading booklist. Great to be there!" and "Ooh, apparently I've also been recommend by School Library Journal (US) as a "tween" alternative to TWILIGHT. I'm having a good day today!"<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-274" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">♫♬♫♪ I just got a letter ♫♬♫♪</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 22 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ourcrew/where/where.html" rel="self" title="Where Are You"><img class="imageStyle" alt="twins" src="twins.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>In case anyone doubted the address I gave for the Captain is correct.  I just received a note back from him.<br />Yipee a letter that is not a bill or another form to fill it.  It really made my day.  Thank you Justin.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-275" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Your ideas</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 10 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-tempesttwins.php">TempestTwins</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ideas/ideas.html" rel="self" title="Your Ideas"><img class="imageStyle" alt="twins" src="twins.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>I would like to thank everyone who contributes to this website.  Especially the Dirty Dolphin under Your ideas.<br /><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-271" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Who's the girl with the black heart tattoo?</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Saturday, 09 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/girlwiththeblackhearttattoo/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="Empire Of Night" src="Empire.jpg" width="74" height="113" /></a></div>On the Vampirate Blog (<a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/merrychristmaswritingisover/" rel="external" title="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/merrychristmaswritingisover/">www.vampirates.co.uk</a>) the Captain has announced who is the person on the left hand side of the skull.<br />Which makes me wonder even more what is going to happen in the next book.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-272" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Happy New Year</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 01 January 2010 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-side-tracked.php">Side Tracked</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ourcrew/where/where.html" rel="self" title="Where Are You"><img class="imageStyle" alt="twins" src="twins.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>Happy New Year.<br /><br /></div></div>
